<p>The combination of LoRA, Flash Attention 2, Deepspeed ZeRO-2, and bfloat=
16 precision enables efficient training of the 7B parameter model on standa=
rd GPU hardware. LoRA specifically reduces the number of trainable paramete=
rs from ~7 billion to only the adapter parameters plus the classification h=
ead.</p>
