<p>While not explicitly specified in the provided configuration files, stan=
dard LoRA implementations for Mistral models typically target the attention=
 query and value projection matrices (<code class=3D"rounded-sm bg-[#e5e5e5=
] px-[0.25rem] py-[0.20rem] text-xs font-normal leading-[15px] before:hidde=
n after:hidden dark:bg-[#484848]/30">q_proj</code>, <code class=3D"rounded-=
